Notes
-----

Adds moodbar support (just like in Amarok).
For more informations see http://amarok.kde.org/wiki/Moodbar


Features
--------

* Moodbar column on track list.

* Seek slider with current's song mood as background .

* Background process to detect moods of entire collection.


Requirements
------------

* banshee >= 1.5.1
* gstreamer >= 0.10
* fftw3f >= 0.7.28
* moodbar binary

If you have the above, you almost definitely have the required dependencies.


Known Issues
------------

* On start it may take few seconds to load all moods to memory so, some moodbar
  cells may be blank for a moment.
